{"tid":2488284,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"Metal Build 討論區 ( 87 ) : 好快就知X1FC究竟值唔值三萬羊","createTime":"2021-04-14T06:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:51:57.000Z","uid":8971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86a90f33242908c76e50dded40765b8494447bdd","tid":2488284,"uid":8971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">請善用會員及不推文模式</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQnnjwvzZwUTQYmSw4rLiNAaNhJJ1kesSkSbybAWgJwqv?filename=yahrNA3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyahrNA3.png&h=75b77615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb6M1e9k9Dpwg7jWrcUQ4WyKGRiTxNyQKVD3jAqehkHn1?filename=6QdgyEC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QdgyEC.png&h=c4dba4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">所 有 投 資 涉 及 風 險 。投 資 者 須 注 意 ， M B 、 M R 、 G F F M C 及 解 体 匠 機 之 價 格 可 升 亦 可 跌 ， 而 所 呈 列 的 過 往 表 現 資 料 並 不 表 示 將 來 亦 會 有 類 似 的 表 現 。 投 資 者 在 作 出 任 何 投 資 決 定 前 ， 應 詳 細 閱 讀 相 關 產 品 之 銷 售 文 件 及 條 款 細 則 ( 包 括 當 中 所 載 之 風 險 因 素 之 全 文 ) 。<br />\n<br />\n本 P O S T 並 未 經 香 港 黃 店 及 玩 具 炒 賣 事 務 監 察 委 員 會 或 任 何 監 管 機 構 審 核 。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">Metal Build派貨表</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsp.tamashii.jp%2Fitem_brand%2Fmetal_build%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=e31bde7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">置頂問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂展限？<br />\nA:每年日本秋葉原Tamashii Nation 展覽的會場限定版除左上面提個盒Trans-am OOR，全部都在展後推出相同的魂限<br />\n<br />\nQ: XXX邊到仲有得訂？XXX信得過嗎？<br />\nA: 宜家成日有人問呢間點 嗰間信唔信得過 都係嗰句<br />\n<br />\n淆嘅唔好訂 信嘅就比錢<br />\n<br />\n我地撚知佢有冇貨派咩 做左咁多年人 買件野都要教嘅 有啲擺明冇息貸款都要衝嘅真係幫你唔到<br />\n循例戴番個頭盔 平價買到係開心 唔難保真係有小店為左做起個名吸引客源會低訂價賺少啲 呢啲冇人知<br />\n<br />\n信不信由你<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我都知冇咩可能有正價，只係想平少少入手魂展命運姐<br />\nA: online搶到死連埋運費都要$2000<br />\n咁你話$2100附近嗰啲，除咗係開善堂我諗唔到係啲咩<br />\n<br />\n咁當然我唔排除真係有大慈善家玩具店<br />\n<br />\nQ: 日版通販邊到有得訂？<br />\nA: 本post只推薦日本屋，暖男包裝完美八角<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://www.nippon-yasan.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nippon-yasan.com&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=43db8950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nippon-yasan.com</a><br />\n<br />\nQ:出貨未？<br />\nA:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaozBJrDicMHVQWUBLJ4ctzYZvSKeW9xYYfKcRmTuVfMg?filename=LybXR00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLybXR00.png&h=6e07a75a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">Preparation in progress</span><br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂限？<br />\nA:經p-bandai 網上訂購的限定版<br />\n<br />\nQ: 魂限邊到訂？<br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.hk&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=26517e12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.jp&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=86838da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.jp</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 日魂訂完野個個月都扣我信用卡錢即係點？<br />\nA: 佢只係試你張卡同hold limit，出貨嗰個月先會真係扣數<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂普通販賣？<br />\nA:即就咁普通係鋪頭賣買既產品<br />\n<br />\nQ:咩版最好QC?<br />\nA:無論行、日、亞，QC都一樣，同為made in China<br />\n<br />\nQ: 行版通販邊到有得訂？<br />\nA: 行貨睇鋪頭心情有時唔開訂直接賣現賺盡啲，就算開都唔定時，只可以做mon post達人<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊度買<br />\nA:邊到買都得，記得抵制精品<br />\n<br />\nQ:買日定行<br />\nA:無分別<br />\n<br />\nQ: 飛西點分正版定老翻？<br />\nA: 老翻本體塊面個兩條線無咁正，散氣口少左條刻線，背部出氣口多左兩點 (下圖轉自貼吧)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYJ1PzVr9jUr4BkvJyWMAukrNK7oLAnPUqyTVbw8DBBk3?filename=Y9yAGVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9yAGVG.jpg&h=ac5cf559&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSsofGJTrEMmHidbNiYYzZscuXy68RN5Hk5k1D66AYrqs?filename=3Y2qjHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Y2qjHn.jpg&h=ad464aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZex7BhycmoDYvCULC9U4tBy4V5W4wmnXmmef4Brwjw5?filename=qXwZo83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXwZo83.jpg&h=05d38685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 突擊自由Soul Blue點分正版定老翻<br />\nA: 頭同膊頭都易分，詳細就睇下評測<br />\n<a href=\"https://post.m.smzdm.com/p/a783wd65/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpost.m.smzdm.com%2Fp%2Fa783wd65%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=edef4fc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://post.m.smzdm.com/p/a783wd65/</a>"},{"pid":"452f3d856f5447dc98542256941696dd193199b6","tid":2488284,"uid":8971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上係1/100合金老翻既list<br />\n1/72唔列了 因為on9都知官方無出到<br />\n如有錯漏 交比巴打補充<br />\n<br />\nQ: 命運點分正版定老翻？<br />\nA: 詳細比較，殘體注意<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20180521/20180521G19ONX.html?pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20180521%2F20180521G19ONX.html%3Fpc&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=842a6bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20180521/20180521G19ONX.html?pc</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 00R點分正版定老翻？<br />\nA: 等FB人稱教主嘅達人教你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a6e77bde066150718d5b7dd6c2a4783a53cf73","tid":2488284,"uid":8971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img